#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:49
msgid "Hot Cue:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:51
msgid "**1:** Set and play (by holding it) from Hot Cue 1"
