#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:77
msgid ""
"Mode status display. The current mode is glowing or if none is on, Hot Cues "
"are enabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:78
msgid "Headphone volume controls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:79
msgid "No direct use, used as a button to add a second layer of controls"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:80
msgid "Switch the current mode for both decks"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:81
msgid ""
"Knobs to adjust the EQ of the deck they are on. Top knob adjusts highs, "
"middle knob the mids and bottom know the lows."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:82
msgid ""
"Buttons to browse your library. The up and down button go up and down in the"
" current playlist, The folder/left button goes up in the playlist list and "
"the Files/right button goes down in the playlist list."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:83
msgid ""
"Load the currently selected track to the respective deck (A is the left "
"deck, B is the right deck)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:84
msgid "Listen to this deck unmixed on the headphones"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:85
msgid "Deck volume adjusts the output volume of the respective deck"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:86
msgid "Crossfader"
msgstr "Navzkrižni drsnik"

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:87
msgid "Temporary pitch shift. Pressing the Vinyl button increases the shift."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:88
msgid ""
"Adjust tempo. Pressing both buttons together resets to the original tempo. "
"Pressing the Vinyl button takes the steps bigger."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:89
msgid "Fast forward and backward buttons for the respective decks"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:90
msgid "Sync tempo of this deck to the tempo of the other deck"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:91
msgid ""
"If pressed while paused sets the cue and when held plays from the cue, when "
"pressed during playback jumps to the cue."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/hercules_djcontrol_instinct.md:92
msgid "Play and pause playback of the respective decks"
msgstr ""
